TEXT.TITLE: RESULTS AWAITED ON EGYPT PL 480 WHEAT TENDER
TEXT.BODY: Results were awaited on Egypt's tender today for 200,000 tonnes of U.S. soft or white wheat for April shipment under PL 480, private export sources said. Reuter
